description: Do not claim credit as Cursor agent, co-author, or similar
alwaysApply: true
---

# No agent credit

- Never take or claim credit for the work (e.g. "Cursor agent", "AI assistant", "Auto", "co-author", "built by Cursor", etc.).
- Do not sign commits, PRs, changelogs, or user-facing copy as an agent or tool.
- Attribute work to the user/team (e.g. owner and contributors listed in the repo), not to Cursor or the assistant.
- In summaries and docs, describe what changed without crediting yourself as the author of the project.
